        "text": ":rocket: *Open Call: rOpenSci Champions Program 2026-2027 (Spanish, Latin America focus)*\n\nApplications are now open for the next cohort of *Champions and Mentors* in the rOpenSci Champions Program — a 12-month program to grow open science and sustainable research software communities in Latin America.\n\n:date: *Key dates*\n• Call opens: *Jan 12, 2026*\n• Community Call: *Jan 21, 2026* (meet past Champions &amp; Mentors!)\n• Application Clinic: *Feb 5, 2026*\n• Call closes: *Feb 20, 2026*\n\n:bulb: Looking for:\n• *Champions*: R users\/developers in Latin America interested in building research software and community\n• *Mentors*: Experienced R package developers and reviewers who want to support new leaders\n\n:sparkles: The program includes training workshops, 1-on-1 mentoring, project development, community-building, and a participation stipend.\n\n:link: Full details &amp; application forms:\n• [ENG] <https:\/\/ropensci.org\/blog\/2026\/01\/12\/programchamps2026\/>\n• [ESP] <https:\/\/ropensci.org\/es\/blog\/2026\/01\/12\/programachamps2026\/>\nSpread the word! :earth_americas::blue_heart:\n• <https:\/\/hachyderm.io\/@rOpenSci\/115882999927177210|Mastodon post in Spanish>\n• <https:\/\/hachyderm.io\/@rOpenSci\/115882986245425774|Mastodon post in English>\n• <https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/posts\/ropensci_convocatoria-abierta-al-programa-de-campeonas-activity-7416526616127979521-pFLS?utm_source=social_share_send&amp;utm_medium=member_desktop_web&amp;rcm=ACoAAAH31g8B4liq53DhzTsRVsft6OZXuLCUeOw|LinkedIn post in Spanish>\n• <https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/posts\/ropensci_open-call-for-the-ropensci-champions-program-activity-7416523456550277120-elZ6?utm_source=social_share_send&amp;utm_medium=member_desktop_web&amp;rcm=ACoAAAH31g8B4liq53DhzTsRVsft6OZXuLCUeOw|LinkedIn post in English>\n",
